video.title: Love
video.synopsis: Rebellious Mickey and good-natured Gus navigate the thrills and agonies of modern relationships in this bold comedy co-created by Judd Apatow.

episodes.synopsis: While recovering from nasty breakups with their exes, Mickey makes a scene at a church and Gus stumbles into a confusing sexual encounter.
episodes.title: It Begins

episodes.synopsis: After Gus steps in to help Mickey out of a jam, the two end up on a bizarre odyssey through the streets of L.A.
episodes.title: One Long Day

episodes.synopsis: Gus faces a make-or-break situation at work, while Mickey navigates a dicey new dynamic with her boss.
episodes.title: Tested

episodes.synopsis: Mix-ups and meltdowns abound when Mickey invites Gus to a party and comes face-to-face with mistakes from her past.
episodes.title: Party in the Hills

episodes.synopsis: As Mickey tries to get her life back on track, Gus takes his date with Bertie to hilarious extremes.
episodes.title: The Date

episodes.synopsis: A newly confident Gus turns heads on set, while a disturbing day at the radio station leaves Mickey feeling reckless.
episodes.title: Andy

episodes.synopsis: Gus sets out to dazzle Mickey on their first real date, but the night doesn't go quite as he planned.
episodes.title: Magic

episodes.synopsis: As Mickey frets over the fallout from their date, a new guest shakes things up at Gus's movie night jam session.
episodes.title: Closing Title Song

episodes.synopsis: Gus gets exciting news at work, but a surprise visit from Mickey sends the day spiraling in a new direction.
episodes.title: The Table Read

episodes.synopsis: Troubles keep mounting for Gus as he gets a taste of life in the writers' room. Meanwhile, a new crisis pushes Mickey to the breaking point.
episodes.title: The End of the Beginning

episodes.synopsis: After coming clean to Gus, Mickey tries to head home to decompress. But an unexpected turn of events keeps them out together late into the night.
episodes.title: On Lockdown

episodes.synopsis: While Gus heads to a bar with his guy friends, a restless Mickey stirs up trouble at a dinner party full of couples.
episodes.title: Friends Night Out

episodes.synopsis: Mickey tries to help her work buddy Truman out of a sticky situation, and an on-set accident rattles the "Witchita" cast and crew.
episodes.title: While You Were Sleeping

episodes.synopsis: A quiet night turns trippy when Mickey convinces Gus, Bertie and Randy to sample her leftover psychedelic mushrooms.
episodes.title: Shrooms

episodes.synopsis: On a day of spontaneous adventures, Mickey and Gus open up about their pasts and begin to let go of their fears.
episodes.title: A Day

episodes.synopsis: Big news on the "Witchita" set leaves Gus caught in the middle of a family dispute over Arya's future. Mickey grows suspicious of Randy's motives.
episodes.title: Forced Hiatus

episodes.synopsis: While Mickey schmoozes with her new corporate bosses at a radio station party, Gus strikes up an unlikely friendship with Dr. Greg.
episodes.title: The Work Party

episodes.synopsis: Gus joins Mickey for an outing with her dad but soon realizes the father-daughter dynamic is more complicated than she let on.
episodes.title: Marty Dobbs

episodes.synopsis: While housesitting at a friend's mansion, Gus and Mickey host a "Witchita" viewing party. But brewing tensions threaten to spoil the fun.
episodes.title: Housesitting

episodes.synopsis: As Gus heads off to the set of Arya's action film and Mickey dives into a big project at work, new cracks appear in their relationship.
episodes.title: Liberty Down

episodes.synopsis: Mickey bonds with her ex, while Gus makes a desperate bid to patch things up with the film director. Bertie has a revelation.
episodes.title: The Long D

episodes.synopsis: With Gus back home, Mickey realizes she needs to make a decision. But her attempt to straighten out her love life only creates more chaos.
episodes.title: Back in Town

episodes.synopsis: Randy pressures Mickey, Gus and Bertie into a couples weekend at his cousin's sweet Palm Springs pad. But nothing about the house is as advertised.
episodes.title: Palm Springs Getaway

episodes.synopsis: While Mickey rides a wave of good news at work, Gus tries to spread some cheer around the tense "Witchita" set -- with demoralizing results.
episodes.title: Winners and Losers

episodes.synopsis: Gus helps a stressed-out Arya gear up for a big scene, while Mickey tries to salvage Dr. Greg's disastrous book-signing event.
episodes.title: Arya and Greg

episodes.synopsis: Gus realizes he's facing a major relationship test when Mickey falls sick just as he's heading out on a horror movie location tour with friends.
episodes.title: I'm Sick

episodes.synopsis: After a disappointing start to her first birthday in America, Bertie winds up on an action-packed LA adventure with a kindred spirit.
episodes.title: Bertie's Birthday

episodes.synopsis: Gus struggles to keep the actors and crew on task as he starts shooting his movie. Mickey sets out to show an old friend she's changed.
episodes.title: Directing

episodes.synopsis: When Gus bumps into an ex at a wedding, Mickey realizes there's a lot she still doesn't know about his past.
episodes.title: Sarah from College

episodes.synopsis: A stunt audition inspires Chris to reconnect with Bertie. Dr. Greg begs for a spot on Stellas show, and Gus asks Arya for a favor.
episodes.title: Stunt Show

episodes.synopsis: As Gus prepares for his band's first gig and a trip back home to South Dakota, Mickey wonders if its time for her to meet the Cruikshank clan.
episodes.title: You're My Gran Torino

episodes.synopsis: Back in the land of guns, cornhole and pickle wheels, Gus makes a critical relationship blunder. A plumbing crisis turns awkward for Bertie.
episodes.title: The Cruikshanks

episodes.synopsis: Gus scrambles to stop Mickey from skipping town before his parents' party. But the day only yields more embarrassing revelations about his past.
episodes.title: Anniversary Party

episodes.synopsis: As Mickey and Gus think seriously about their future, a spontaneous trip to Catalina Island brings together a motley group of their friends.
episodes.title: Catalina
